resources.string:
"Payment: The automatic renewal includes continuous yearly and monthly subscription. After you confirm your purchase, you will deduct fees from your Alipay account:
Renewal: Alipay will deduct fees one day before the expiration of each subscription package, and the subscription cycle will be postponed for one cycle after successful deduction;
Cancel Renewal: If you want to cancel the renewal, you can turn off the automatic renewal function in the renewal order details of Value added Services - Orders at any time before the next deduction. Cancelling will no longer automatically renew"
